und $6-10, from legitimate sources like GOG.\n\n**In Summary:**\n\nThe safest and most recommended way to download RollerCoaster Tycoon 1 (Deluxe) is through GOG.com. You get a DRM-free, optimized version of the game, and you support the creators. Be wary of illegal download sites and abandonware sites, as they pose a risk to your computer and are often illegal.\n",
